  "description": "<i>Dark Arms: Beast Buster 1999</i> is a RPG for the Neo Geo Pocket Color. It's a spin-off from the arcade game <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/beast-busters\">Beast Busters</a>.<br><br>Parallel to our world we find the Dark Realm. As the player, you find access to this parallel dimension after signing a pact with the Master of the Dark Realm. In his realm, you are supposed to catch monsters. These can be fed to your biological weapons: Dark Arms. You weapons gain abilities from consumed monsters and can evolve into more powerful equipment. You can also find seeds in the Dark Realm that turn into new weapons.<br><br>The game features puzzles that have to be solved and a wide array of undead monsters that can be fed to your Dark Arms.",
